{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "HTMX Template Validation Hook",
  "description": "Validates HTMX templates for proper patterns and Alpine.js integration",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileEdited",
    "patterns": [
      "verifast_app/templates/**/*.html",
      "templates/**/*.html"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "HTMX template modified. Please validate:\n\n1. **HTMX Attributes**: Check hx-get/hx-post URLs exist in urls.py, verify hx-target selectors exist\n2. **CSRF Protection**: Ensure HTMX POST requests include {% csrf_token %}\n3. **Alpine.js Integration**: Validate x-data components and event handlers\n4. **Progressive Enhancement**: Check forms work without JavaScript\n\nFocus on critical URLs: speed_reader_init, speed_reader_complete, quiz_start, add_comment. Report issues and suggest fixes."
  }
}